{"tid":1547413,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（極愛國） 銅鑼灣新記車仔麵","createTime":"2019-09-06T16:03:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T07:29:38.000Z","uid":275202,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"09b889298d0def1f5bd4e99be9c5975749b88feb","tid":1547413,"uid":275202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:03:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/06/235230_ca5c61c4d356264f94775ad8a46d5d16.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F06%2F235230_ca5c61c4d356264f94775ad8a46d5d16.png&h=366f34fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今晚入去食野<br />\n成間餐廳由老闆到員工都極藍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：老闆<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：員工<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：宜家啲後生仔唔會食嘢㗎啦，搞到生意差左好多呀！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：嗰班𡃁仔全部有時間都出去遊行啦！咁多錢收<br />\n行前少少又話唔知幾多錢！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：係囉！上過鏡又話唔知幾多錢，就咁出去普通行都有$5000啦！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：咁噤多錢搵，你唔出去行？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我地腳踏實地！唔做埋晒呢啲咁嘅嘢㗎！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：咁你地有無真憑實據啊？有無證據證明啊？喺度亂講！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：如果證實到嘅我就攞哂啲錢啦！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：咁你哋冇證實又喺度亂咁講<br />\n<br />\n之後無人再應我<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999<br />\n<br />\n如果大家對餐廳嘅衛生情況有隱憂嘅，都應該聯絡食環講下囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9dc9402f9048d3eab5a73afb74306110e3ba4c3","tid":1547413,"uid":27